{"tid":2052989,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：籲勿「講港獨」(明明稻草人黎 唔係黎真下話）","createTime":"2020-06-06T02:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T02:44:28.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e25b100085ced977ec8515a67aabd76bd6a573ca","tid":2052989,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:38:49.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊：港獨猖獗令國安現缺口使香港成為風險點<br />\n06.06.2020 10:02<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊出席本台節目時說，本港去年發生反修例事件以來，暴力橫行，恐怖活動慢慢浮現，有人肆無忌憚推動港獨，令國家安全出現缺口，從國家層面是不能接受。<span style=\"color: gold;\">她希望市民發表意見時，要回歸和平、客觀和理性討論，無謂嘗試「講港獨」。</span><br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊又說，客觀事實是香港回歸20幾年來，都未能就《基本法》23條立法，在可預見的時間內都做不到，同時有很多人不斷嘗試做危害國家安全的事，甚至令香港變成風險點，很大機會被人利用作分裂國家的基地，現時從國家層面處理國家安全問題是合理的方法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1301172&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1301172%26csid%3D261_341&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGUV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=cefbb154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1301172&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5ba36cd45db72f203e364befb4a31e868211cbc6","tid":2052989,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"假戲真做，高手"},{"pid":"3baed91db92804b0b22e8c7b37826709b21e2b53","tid":2052989,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:40:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f88f08dbf128bd5edbcf90d241b845bfc766bbb4","tid":2052989,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"成班玻璃心，乜撚都話恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfbb90b65246d7147a5f13dbdba6c20ed272450","tid":2052989,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3baed91db92804b0b22e8c7b37826709b21e2b53","tid":2052989,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"